      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "content": "### Fishystuff Local Observability\nUse this dashboard as the local entrypoint for the repo-managed telemetry stack.\n\n- `Loki` is the default datasource for correlated logs.\n- `Prometheus` scrapes Vector for spanmetrics, service metrics and host metrics.\n- `Jaeger` is still the best view for trace detail and Service Performance Monitoring.\n\nOpen the map page, then keep this dashboard and Jaeger side by side while tracing requests and runtime metrics.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "Overview",
      "type": "text"
    },
